      <title>亿万富翁 7-Eleven 继承人的收购要约随后匆忙改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/billionaire-7-eleven-heirs-buyout-bid-came-after-hasty-u-turn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在三个月前，日本 7-Eleven 连锁店的继承人伊藤润郎还在向投资者推销 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/billionaire-7-eleven-heirs-buyout-bid-came-after-hasty-u-turn</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金 GCQ 每年上涨 30%，押注日本云软件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/hedge-fund-gcq-up-30-a-year-bets-on-japan-cloud-software</link>
      <description><![CDATA[GCQ Funds Management 认为，日本云计算行业的参与者能够继续提高价格，希望能够在此基础上再创两年前成立以来 30% 的年化收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/hedge-fund-gcq-up-30-a-year-bets-on-japan-cloud-software</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
